# Pre-Report Documentation Sync (Mandatory)

## Contract
Before forming any task completion report (summary, "выполнено", итоги), the agent MUST follow id:sk-9e4f2a (process-pre-report-docs-sync).

## Checklist (run before report)
1. Update docs/AIS with all changes made.
2. Add new causality hashes to causality-registry.md.
3. Create skills if explicit automation fragments or specific approaches were discovered.
4. Update contracts if new gates/config were introduced.
5. Only then form the report.

## Violation
Report without completing the checklist = contract violation. Docs and causalities must stay live-actual.
